description: Amundi Global Aggregate Bond UCITS ETF DR - HEDGED EUR (C) seeks to replicate, as closely as possible the performance of the Bloomberg Global Aggregate value hedged EUR Index (the "Index"), whether the trend is rising or falling. The Sub-Fund aims to achieve a level of tracking error of the Sub-Fund and its Index that will not normally exceed 1%. For further information on index rules, please refer to the fund prospectus or KID.
name: Amundi Global Aggregate Bond UCITS ETF DR - HEDGED EUR (C)
